N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 9 §§ 296-2.6 - Personal injury or property damage

State Regulations

If a visitor is injured or their vehicle is damaged in
a State operated parking area, they must report the details of the incident on
forms available at any parking attendant station, as soon as possible. In the
event a parking attendant is not on duty the visitor should contact the State

Police or local police agency. Notes
